data.description: Well maintained single level home located on a private setting in SE Hillsboro. Fantastic 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom floor plan with excellent flow, vaulted ceilings, and lots of natural light. Several recent improvements including 50 year roof, Hot water heater, plumbing, inground lawn irrigation, kitchen range, new backyard tuff shed, new carpet and paint. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances. Remarkably private, low maintenance yard perfect for entertaining and gardening. The home with it's solar panels has very low energy costs and scored a perfect 10 on it's energy score. Move in ready! Open house 10/28, Sat: 1-3pm.
